ActCanadian Tourism Commission Act
PrecisApproval of the re-appointment by the Minister of Industry of BHAGWANT S. PARMAR of Brockville, Ontario, as a director of the Board of Directors of the Canadian Tourism Commission, to hold office during pleasure on a part-time basis for a term of four years, effective October 30, 2009.
